{"tid":2013226,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2019年06月21日 鄧炳強: 小心記者　唔好蝕章 呼籲警員看到身穿記者反光衣的人時要「小心少少」","createTime":"2020-05-12T07:09:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T07:32:10.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"78c45400b1a8e3608646cd55d4088d7b9282acad","tid":2013226,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:09:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190621/20709634\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190621%2F20709634&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmID442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=14fb4f77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190621%2F20709634&h=24deca61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190621/20709634</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方於6.12暴力清場期間，多次對在場採訪的傳媒惡言相向，甚至以暴力對待。根據《蘋果》取得的錄音，疑為警務處副處長（行動）鄧炳強與駐守政府總部的警員會面時，指部份傳媒針對警察，「成日話我哋夥計講咩『記你老母』，咁我哋明白到呢啲人嘅心態係啲咩嘢呢，就盡量唔好蝕章畀佢」，反映警方仍然對傳媒抱持敵意。"},{"pid":"d3acdd141fef5571d49178d3b5561a25a5729896","tid":2013226,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:10:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190620/large/1561028522_872c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190620%2Flarge%2F1561028522_872c.png&h=82b6a1e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f209dccfaec15e56cdeb4cd62418d9e0c8e2c4b","tid":2013226,"uid":275903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:32:10.000Z","msg":"而家唔撚同啦<br />\n一枝警棍仆過去 再送多張告票比你"}]}